705646f-b.title: Brooklyn: McDonald Avenue - Avenue T
705646f-b.text:
2180 McDonald Eve., at the N.W. corner of Ave. T, showing a view
of a Greek American Democratic Club. The side with the sign is
Esunnef.--o.
February 24, 1931.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
The same, at a later date. The sign has been altered.
April 25, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
